This paper is likely to belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-category as it discusses performance optimization techniques for large-scale applications using LLVM framework. Additionally, it may also belong to the sub-categories of Architecture (cs.AR) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) as it deals with optimizing code layout for data-center applications. Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) are also possible sub-categories as the paper discusses the use of sample-based profiling to improve performance.
